name: Individual Kaleido 05
description:
Individual Kaleido 05 with a seed based on the owner's tezos-address, renders differently for everyone.
If you own the OBJKT, use UP-ARROW or Click/Tap to switch to alternate figure.

Uses the hicdex API and therefore depends on it. This is all experimental and might break in the future. - @TeNinEightNFTs
